            <p class="text-lg font-bold text-[#073B4C]">In a Nutshell</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 max-w-4xl mx-auto">Social constructionism explains <span class="text-[#FF6B6B] font-bold">what</span> cultural ideas we create, intersectionality reveals <span class="text-[#FFD166] font-bold">how</span> our identities overlap within those ideas, and fairy tales show us <span class="text-[#06D6A0] font-bold">how</span> these ideas are passed down through generations.</p>
        </footer>

